title: Fidel Castro's son kills himself after depression
text:
Fidel Castro's son kills himself after depression 12:24pm GMT - 01:18 
Fidel Castro Diaz-Balart - the eldest son of the late Cuban revolutionary leader - has committed suicide after months of treatment for depression. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
